19Ps 9:1 [For the choir director£∫ A psalm of David, to be sung to the tune "Death of the Son"] I will praise you, LORD, with all my heart; I will tell of all the marvelous things you have done.
19Ps 9:2 I will be filled with joy because of you. I will sing praises to your name, O Most High.
