19Ps 9:6 The enemy is finished, in endless ruins; the cities you uprooted are now forgotten.
19Ps 9:7 But the LORD reigns forever, executing judgment from his throne.
19Ps 9:8 He will judge the world with justice and rule the nations with fairness.
19Ps 9:9 The LORD is a shelter for the oppressed, a refuge in times of trouble.
