19Ps 10:14 But you see the trouble and grief they cause. You take note of it and punish them. The helpless put their trust in you. You defend the orphans.
19Ps 10:15 Break the arms of these wicked, evil people! Go after them until the last one is destroyed.
19Ps 10:16 The LORD is king forever and ever! The godless nations will vanish from the land.
