23Is 42:13 The Lord will march forth like a mighty hero; he will come out like a warrior, full of fury. He will shout his battle cry and crush all his enemies.
23Is 42:14 He will say, °∞I have long been silent; yes, I have restrained myself. But now, like a woman in labor, I will cry and groan and pant.
