23Is 44:26 But I carry out the predictions of my prophets! By them I say to Jerusalem, °ÆPeople will live here again,°Ø and to the towns of Judah, °ÆYou will be rebuilt; I will restore all your ruins!°Ø
23Is 44:27 When I speak to the rivers and say, °ÆDry up!°Ø they will be dry.
