23Is 45:1 This is what the Lord says to Cyrus, his anointed one, whose right hand he will empower. Before him, mighty kings will be paralyzed with fear. Their fortress gates will be opened, never to shut again.
23Is 45:2 This is what the Lord says. °∞I will go before you, Cyrus, and level the mountains®Á. I will smash down gates of bronze and cut through bars of iron. / ®ÁAs in Dead Sea Scrolls and Greek version; Masoretic Text reads the swellings
