23Is 45:14 This is what the Lord says. °∞You will rule the Egyptians, the Ethiopians®Á, and the Sabeans. They will come to you with all their merchandise, and it will all be yours. They will follow you as prisoners in chains. They will fall to their knees in front of you and say, °ÆGod is with you, and he is the only God. There is no other.°Ø°± / ®ÁHebrew Cushites
