23Is 47:1 °∞Come down, virgin daughter of Babylon, and sit in the dust. For your days of sitting on a throne have ended. O daughter of Babylonia®Á, never again will you be the lovely princess, tender and delicate. / ®ÁOr Chaldea; also in 47.5
